                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6879" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PJMT-0121</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10626 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">不畏浮云遮望眼，&quot;铁&quot;担重任：全生命周期视角下X集团公司投资项目管理体系创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">No afraid of clouds, &quot;Iron&quot; to bear the burden:Investment project Management Innovation in XN Works Section of X Group Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汪方军，舒伟，王袁玺，高勇，赵利娜，张昕英，吴翠花</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国铁路青藏集团公司西宁工务段</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全生命周期管理理论；投资项目管理；挣值法；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Life cycle management theory; Investment project management; Earned value method</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">根据中央深化国有企业改革的决策部署，深化国铁企业改革、推进体制机制创新、提升铁路企业运营效率和效果、保持资本保值增值是现阶段的重大现实问题。投资项目管理体系持续优化对铁路企业实现降本增效目标以及高质量转型发展具有重要意义。在落实改革的过程中，X铁路集团公司（以下简称“X集团”）将全生命周期管理理论引入投资项目管理全过程重构项目决策机制，在新建项目投资前全面分析成本效益，在项目实施过程中建立监控体系，在项目实施后评价阶段分析差异，为后续投资项目降低投资风险、提高投资效益提供有益的经验。
全生命周期视角下投资项目管理体系是铁路企业投资项目管理的新思路。本案例以X集团为研究对象，运用投融资管理、全生命周期管理和项目管理方法（如挣值法、成本效益法）等管理会计工具，构建出基于全生命周期理论的投资项目管理体系，推动铁路企业投资项目管理水平提升。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">According to the central government&#39;s decision and deployment to deepen the reform of state-owned enterprises, deepening the reform of national railway enterprises, promoting system and mechanism innovation, improving the operation efficiency and effect of railway enterprises, and maintaining the value of capital are major practical problems at this stage. Continuous optimization of the investment project management system is critical for railway enterprises to achieve the goal of lowering costs, increasing efficiency, and promoting high-quality transformation and development. X group company in investment project management must improve the project decision-making mechanism, be clear before a newly built project investment cost and benefit, establish a monitoring system in the process of project implementation, project implementation after the evaluation summary, provide experience for subsequent investment projects, so as to reduce project investment risk and improve the efficiency of the project. To carry out the task of capital preservation and escort expansion.
An investment project management system from the full life cycle perspective is a management concept proposed by combining full life cycle theory with management accounting tools and methods. It&#39;s a novel approach to managing railway enterprise investment projects. Based on a railway group co., LTD. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;X group company&quot;) as the research object, build the lifecycle theory based on the group company investment project management system and promote the railway enterprise investment project management level using investment and financing management and project management methods, such as the earned value method, cost-effective method) management accounting methods, such as tools.
Keywords: Life cycle management theory; Investment project management; Earned value method
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计学》、《商业伦理与企业社会责任》、《项目管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">投资项目管理；铁路投资项目建设过程中的投融资管理；全生命周期管理理论；投资项目管理体系；成本效益法；企业社会责任；财务指标与非财务指标；挣值法；管理会计应用指引；财务信息化手段</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-12</td>
                            </tr>
